    "headline": "Harrah’s Oklahoma Officially Opens in Chandler",
    "summary": "CHANDLER, Okla., April 09, 2026--Harrah’s Oklahoma is officially open, marking the first Caesars Entertainment-managed property in the state and a new destination for tourism and entertainment in Oklahoma. Developed in partnership with the Iowa Tribe of Oklahoma, the casino celebrated its grand opening with a ribbon-cutting ceremony featuring tribal and Caesars leadership, first gaming moments, local celebrity appearances, live entertainment and a fireworks finale.",
